  "response": "There are several reputable solar panel installation providers near Nicasio, California. Below are a few options to consider:\n\n1. **Sunrun Solar** - Sunrun is a well-known company that offers solar installation services throughout California, including areas near Nicasio.\n\n2. **SolarCraft** - Based in Novato, SolarCraft is a local provider with extensive experience in solar panel installations in Marin County.\n\n3. **SolarCity (now part of Tesla)** - SolarCity provides a range of solar services and installations and operates throughout California.\n\n4. **SunPower by Solar Technologies** - Located in Richmond, CA, SunPower by Solar Technologies offers high-quality solar solutions and serves the broader Bay Area.\n\n5. **Allterra Solar** - Based in San Rafael, Allterra Solar is another nearby provider that offers solar installation services in Marin County.\n\nBefore choosing a provider, I'd recommend researching their reviews, services, and comparing quotes to ensure you find the best option for your needs. Additionally, checking for any local incentives or rebates for solar installations can be beneficial.",
